Workflow for a web application development

1) create a new project in task04 folder using the following commands

npm is the package manager for node
npm uses package manager only for node
- npm init
- npm install --save-dev gulp
- npm install --save-dev gulp-util
- npm install --save-dev gulp-less
- npm install --save-dev path
- npm install --save-dev gulp-coffee
- npm install --save-dev gulp-concat
- npm install --save-dev gulp-uglify
- npm install --save-dev gulp-livereload
- npm install --save-dev tiny-lr
- npm install -g http-server

2) Make folder structure like follow

components
  coffee
    script.coffee
  less
    main.less
  lib
  scripts
    common.js
    page1.js
css
js
index.html
package.json
gulpfile.js


<--this is for connecting to git proxy not for Gulp, gulp need  path user variable (C:\Users\YourName\AppData\Roaming\npm;C:\Program Files\nodejs\  and run npm install -g gulp  )->
@echo off
