echo GIT proxy set.
echo on


You need to add the viewport meta tag to the <head> element, to ensure proper rendering and touch zooming on mobile devices.
1)<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
 or
 <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, 
                                     initial-scale=1.0, 
                                     maximum-scale=1.0, 
                                     user-scalable=no">
									 
2)<img src="..." class="img-responsive" alt="Responsive image">
3)scaffolding.less.
4)Normalize.css for cross browers
5)By wrapping any .table in .table-responsive class,
